NBER Patents Data:

These data comprise detail information on almost 3 million U.S. patents granted between January 1963 and December 1999, 
all citations made to these patents between 1975 and 1999 (over 16 million), and a reasonably broad match of patents 
to Compustat (the data set of all firms traded in the U.S. stock market)

URL: http://data.nber.org/patents/
  
Data Files:

  1. acite75_99.zip
  2. apat63_99.zip
  3. ainventor.zip 
  
